1. Use 
ping
 to check basic connectivity.
eg: ping google.com
2. Use 
dig
 to verify DNS resolution.
eg:dig amazon.in

3. Use 
traceroute
 if connectivity fails.
eg:traceroute google.com

4. Use 
ss
 to confirm the service is listening locally.
5. Use 
nc
 to test remote port access.
6. Use 
curl
 to test the application response.
eg:
curl -I https://google.com
